# 5001fecae00842889e702b8b8dcfab12
#: ../../developer-guide/api/functions/TSHttpTxnInfoIntGet.en.rst:31
msgid ""
":c:func:`TSHttpTxnInfoIntGet` returns arbitrary integer-typed info about "
"a transaction as defined in :c:type:`TSHttpTxnInfoKey`. The API will be "
"part of a generic API umbrella that can support returning arbitrary info "
"about a transaction using custom log tags. It works on multiple hooks "
"depending on the requested info. For example, cache related info may be "
"available only at or after :c:data:`TS_HTTP_CACHE_LOOKUP_COMPLETE_HOOK` "
"hook."
msgstr ""

# a4ed6822cd2742898976ea7a66abbb16
#: ../../developer-guide/api/functions/TSHttpTxnInfoIntGet.en.rst:36
msgid ""
"The :c:type:`TSHttpTxnInfoKey` currently supports the below integer-based"
" info about a transaction"
msgstr ""

