#: ../../developer-guide/api/functions/TSHttpTxnInfoIntGet.en.rst:50
msgid ""
"This info is available at or after "
":c:data:`TS_HTTP_CACHE_LOOKUP_COMPLETE_HOOK` hook. A value of 1 indicates"
